Class MkTreeHeader

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PageHeader
    public class MkTreeHeader
extends TreeIndexHeader
    Encapsulates the header information for subclasses of AbstractMkTreeUnified. This information is needed for persistent storage.
    Since:
    0.2
    Author:
    Elke Achtert
